title: EP 79: Brooklyn 2 Los Angeles w/ Doggie Diamonds
itunes:title: EP 79: Brooklyn 2 Los Angeles w/ Doggie Diamonds
description:
On this episode we have Brooklyn's Doggie Diamonds on the concrete couch. We discuss the rise of the Bloods and Crips in New York, his relationship with the late Notorious B.I.G. and Lil Kim, his run in with Tupac and why New Yorker's initially thought West Coast rappers were p-ssy. Tap in to hear this and more.
